---
title: Golden Chicken & Roast Veggie Medley with Lemon Yoghurt Hummus
description: Are you ready for a tasty yoghurt that goes perfectly with spiced chicken? If the answer is yes, then may we recommend the zesty hummus yoghurt to drizzle over everything, including the roast veggies, tossed into a salad.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
